task.summary: Default task
Add basic set_icon() functionality in ManageCategories.
Add enable/disable behavior for the "set icon" button in ManageCategories based on the presence or absence of text.
Add dynamic renaming of category icon file names when changes are made to the name of the category from ManageCategories.
Change the size of the 'set icon' button in ManageCategories to better fit the preferred dimensions of category icons.
Upon re-opening the ManageCategories window, pre-populate it with widgets for existing categories.
When removing a category from the ManageCategories window, the associated data for that category is also removed.
Add category selection when transitioning from the MainWindow window to the ManageFields window.
Move the intermediate add_item code from SelectCategory to MainWindow.
Remove hard-coded categories from SelectCategory and pass in user-created categories instead.
Add initial code to store category field data when transitioning from ManageFields to MainWindow and back.
Overhaul naming scheme of variables in ManageFields.
Pre-populate ManageFields rows with existing category field data.
Change category_icon_names and category_icon_paths from lists to dicts.
Fix a bug where the program crashes when an existing category doesn't have an icon.
Fix a bug where icons aren't matching category names correctly under certain circumstances.
Add the initial code to pre-populate ManageFields with existing combo items.
Fix a bug where removing empty categories causes the program to crash.
Fix a bug where the current row is off by one when adding new or editing existing combo items to a category field.
Fix a bug where field type, rather than combo items, is loaded into the input field in GetComboItems.
Add commas to pre-populated combo items in GetComboItems.
Adjust the formatting of the header in ManageFields.
Rename 'current_row' to 'idx' in init_category_fields in ManageFields.
Remove hardcoded categories and fields (and related code) from AddItem.
Change all instances of 'temp_input' to 'item' in AddItem.
Change all instances of 'get_category_selection()' to 'get_category()' in MainWindow and SelectCategory.
Replace outdated code for initializing category fields in AddItem.
Add a header to AddItem.
Redo the layout in AddItem.
Remove the window title from AddItem.
Remove window hints from the top of the window in AddItem.
Change stylesheet properties for AddItem to better fit current theme.
Remove the title from SelectCategory.
Remove window hints from the top of the window in SelectCategory.
Change stylesheet properties for SelectCategory to better fit current theme.
Simplify SelectCategory layout.
Add header to SelectCategory and update stylesheet.
Adjust SelectCategory widget dimensions and placement.
Integrate the catalog profile and data into the the same structure.
Fix a bug where new catalog items aren't inserted into the catalog.
Convert all key values in ManageCategories and ManageFields to strings.
Insert MainWindow layouts into a dict and optimize init_layout method.
Set the modality to true for all classes except MainWindow.
Change 'header_title' to 'header' and 'header_logo' to 'logo' in MainWindow.
Fix a bug where keys in AddItem are integers instead of strings.
Initialize the first row in ManageFields when there are no fields.
Prevent the first row from being removed in ManageFields.
Fix a bug where the first row in ManageFields isn't initialized when the window opens without data a second time.
Change all instances of 'Media' to 'Category' in MainWindow.
Replace all instances of 'Title' with the appropriate user-created category ID in MainWindow.
